pair_modify     mix arithmetic

bond_style      none
angle_style     none
dihedral_style  none
improper_style  none

read_data       lmp.data

pair_coeff      * *  0.0 0.0

neighbor	2.0 bin
neigh_modify	every 1

timestep        1.0

